				<div class="writing"><h4>Writing</h4>			<div class="assignment-title">Blog Post #8: YouTube Movies from the 1950s (Due November 30)</div>
			<div class="description"><p>Visit <a href="http://youtube.com">YouTube</a> and <a href="http://youtube.com/results?search_query=1950s&search=Search">do a search for &#8220;1950s.&#8221;</a> There will be lots of junk, but also so interesting television advertisements and movie clips from the 1950s. Find one movie and critique it. What kinds of imagery does it use? What is its message? Who is the intended audience? Along with your critique, embed the movie in your post using the code provided by YouTube.</p></div>
